.TH "epf_ntb_bind" 9 "epf_ntb_bind" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
epf_ntb_bind \- Initialize endpoint controller to provide NTB functionality
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" epf_ntb_bind
.BI "(struct pci_epf *epf "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "epf" 12
NTB endpoint function device
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initialize both the endpoint controllers associated with NTB function device.
Invoked when a primary interface or secondary interface is bound to EPC
device. This function will succeed only when EPC is bound to both the
interfaces.
